      <abstract>
        <p>The one-pot synthesis of 3,6-bis(5&#x2019;-bromo-3&#x2019;-indolyl)-1,4-dimethylpiperazine-2,5-dione is reported. Sarcosine anhydride is brominated and immediately reacted with 5-bromoindole to produce the product, which is characterized by <sup>1</sup>H NMR, MS and microanalysis.</p>
      </abstract>
